verson number ALPHA 0.02 

pong for raspberry pi. This is a small one man project to make geniral games for the raspberry pi including and rpg that is still on the drawing board. I will also make windows and mac binarys but for now if you want the game you can compile it form source. you will need the latest pygame compiled with python 3. 

build instructions:
-download and extract source

-in the terminal cd to the directory with the pong.py file

-type (without quotations) "python3 pong.py"

-HAVE FUN

alternetly open in IDLE 3 and compile by pressing F5
